com.jswiff
Class SWFDocument

java.lang.Object
  com.jswiff.SWFDocument
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class SWFDocument
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable

This class represents a Macromedia Flash (SWF) document. Contains an SWF header and a list of tags. Use a SWFReader to parse a file to an SWFDocument instance. Write SWF files using SWFWriter.

See Also:
